Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,第二話 成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好 拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,又看見了 拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不行啊\N我正更換感光玻璃板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,關掉收音機\N我不能集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是波斯托尼亞城堡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏是希爾索斯天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,知道 繼續保持觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,閱兵儀式要趕快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不請自來的客人終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:01:59.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞 恭喜你單獨飛行成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不用奉承我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,除了飛行時間較短以外 你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那邊的不是更厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭對機械的感覺特別敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:17.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是我讓他學駕駛飛機的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞你身為海姆家的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,卻想成為市民軍的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為我有個父親是飛機製造商的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,家裏的事就拜託姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果讓我做官員或商人的夫人那就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的閱兵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要在夏至的前一日舉行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那不是成人式開始的日子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,所以 很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不能去參觀\N你們兩人的成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我要駕駛這架飛機參加閱兵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為你爸爸的設計被採用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好 裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可是 萊因福特老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不讓我的工場生產全部的飛機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,一半以上在他自己的工場裏生產
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 為了量產的設備 要投資很多錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我家從爺爺那一代便開始製造飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:18.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,現在就是得到回報的時候\N也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,感謝戰爭這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果在海戰上出動飛機進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加利亞的領主\N會被嚇得臉色發青啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,注意那邊的機槍\N你們怎麼搞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼閱兵儀式要在那一天舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果在成人節之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也就能以市民軍一員的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,參加閱兵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,討厭！座位很熱！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你坐在後面就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你不覺得熱嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我是司機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真的打算加入市民軍嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也是啊 羅蘭\N加入市民軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我由老爺來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,美雪你也說兩句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞\N你得到爸爸的批准了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我自己的事由我自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人節要努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,閱兵儀式 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今天是我的成人式！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:45.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:46.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你這個孩子真怕痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,露宿山頭跌傷 真蠢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今日非常忙的 趕快換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:57.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是市民軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,全部都會參加諾克斯市的閱兵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,擴音機和探射燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,看著前面嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,靠右行駛 右面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很大規模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比想像中盛大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的閱兵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:32.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在域辛鎮的成人式那天舉行\N這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,公子也有很多事情要考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼這裏靠近大街卻很靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為這裏也用作員工宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可是 不覺得太大嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你們很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,尺寸是一個月前量的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,連一毫米都不會差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是不是瘦了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,越來越像迪安娜陛下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,能參加波斯托尼亞城堡的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你後年也會被邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,而且 今天是成人式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大學那邊如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,還未開學我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,反正只會教些我已知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.52,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想投身社會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這孩子在胡說些什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸你可以幫我問一問嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想在城堡的\N行政府裏工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏的牆壁需要些畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要是兼職\N多少我都能幫你找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想就業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要再談那話題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,閱兵儀式要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,三時一定要去到諾克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你記得遊園會的地點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哦?羅蘭不一起去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為司機不可以坐在貴賓席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你去見諾克斯市的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我沒那打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要緊啊\N因為今日是特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:22.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,向英格歷撤領主\N萊因福特大人敬禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的威風凜凜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加利亞真的會橫渡大西洋進攻這裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是為了預防他們進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:38.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,才需要這種有組織的軍隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真的打算加入市民軍嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟你不想上大學\N想投身社會一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,儀態很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的飛機部隊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,居於地球的人\N為何總是向上望而不向下望?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為他們不想離開地面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果回歸開始了\N你們有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不想作為回歸者登記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也會繼續學習弄麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我要讓大家吃到美味的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我會成為這裏的報社記者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,經過今日的成人節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我便會成為域辛鎮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,飛機部隊呀！數量很多！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,美雪在其中一部飛機上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是航空部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個該不會跟迪安娜回歸軍戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是用來防護加利亞的飛艇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:40.15,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下會最先到達地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜·索雷爾會最後才降落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,域辛鎮的成人式是怎麼樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道啊\N是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 有神秘感才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,或許是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,恩?  禮炮嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:16.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不到加納坦避暑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,請閣下也多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我會考慮 請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在找海姆先生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:33.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,幫我去找狄蘭·海姆先生\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人節結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你有興趣\N在波斯托尼亞城堡工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:43.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個…諾克斯市對我來說太現代化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,域辛鎮比較適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼 我想你幫西多工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,尋礦的工作 現在也需要技術員的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,西多先生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你認識他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是談工作的\N你可以介紹給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,與其上大學學些無謂的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我寧願投身社會實地學習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:12.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,公子 請恕我和次女失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:17.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我和長女會出席晚上的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,請你們專心舉行你們的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉 請你考慮一下幫西多工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威先生怎麼稱呼羅蘭為羅拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他比較適合羅拉這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉你會幫挖掘工西多先生工作嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不是叫羅拉 我叫羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺不停叫你羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏和這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,總共有六處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,腰部以上的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這附近?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要 好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,六處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,還會有人溺水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.59,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,通宵祭典就是整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在WHITE DOLL前\N隨意玩樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,重要的是通宵祭典開始時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,進行的神聖刻印儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…  神聖刻印…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,轉身\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏、這裏、這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在這六處地方刻上聖痕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為WHITE DOLL身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有那形狀的痣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼 為什麼會有那種痕跡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,傳說中是那樣 沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那些聖痕\N是用手指按下去做成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,男人只需要知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你只須要吸引女人的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出發了！抬起神轎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好  去西蓋爾山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老婆也來這裏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:42.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你說過你對新時代有興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但我也喜歡跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我會讓你看看新時代的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,稍後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼 我代表被選中的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在WHITE DOLL面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,進行神聖刻印儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,誰願意跟我一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個湯姆\N真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加油！不要輸給捷克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.59,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是個好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家！快回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭·塞亞克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這就是不用電線\N也能通訊的機器?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是月之民送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有居住於月亮上的種族嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,由於他們想移居地球\N所以我們增強了市民軍來應對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有那麼多人涌來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不僅是英格歷撤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他們還要求我們將\N北阿米利亞大陸的SUNBELT地帶交給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這就是居住在月球的宇宙人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原來你一直那麼辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在哪裏！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍有報告嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是   正在詢問各部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有報告嗎！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒理由能在夜間飛行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也不是市民軍的正式成員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸你造的轟炸機HIPHEAVY\N我也駕駛了很長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你有什麼想法?  西多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在飛機在天空飛行的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,還舉行這種儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,世間的事物非全部講邏輯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,多虧了這儀式\N山上一個人也沒有 正適合調查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒問題吧  羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我…我不清楚   怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你也轉身脫掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,請賜我六個聖痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,聖痕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我剛才交了給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我害羞得快要死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,討厭   今日是成人節
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.52,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你還帶著那種玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是嗎?  因為今晚是最後一晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這…這是什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是水蛭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,用它們在背部刻上聖痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出來了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蓋子可以扔掉 快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我自己會處理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是水蛭\N從以前起就是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,水蛭?\N不需要很著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不這樣做便不能成為大人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你已經遲了兩年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你知道位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,能否像個男子漢般\N完成通宵祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你是否被承認為成人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,又走出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼聲音！?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,諾克斯市的方向明亮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是火的顏色啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的！起火啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂 羅蘭！知道是哪裏嗎！?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,肯定是諾克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,火很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好像整個城市在起火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼?  探射燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:08.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是轟炸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼?\N這幫傢伙認真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,賓湛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,賓湛你回去鎮壓諾克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我去西面戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 市民軍出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的戰鬥力根本不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼你回去 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,認真的嗎！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它在跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 它好像機械啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,BULWAN開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,野蠻人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,別胡鬧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:30.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼！?  還是下山比較好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是艦隊戰級的長距離激光炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:38.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在迪安娜回歸軍的訓練裏見過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭  我們要繼續通宵儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼事！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞和羅蘭被埋起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什麼東西? 發生什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL竟然粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:28.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是駕駛艙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它在動 有東西在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,駕駛艙是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是駕駛的座位 你不覺得很像麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是座位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你說這種東西會動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這是WHITE DOLL啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 那非常的亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你不覺得它好像會動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,絕對是駕駛艙\N這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,頭部剛才好像動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,請你下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這東西靠什麼開動的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,連頭盔也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但控制台很不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,隨便碰它一下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,看起來像手臂的東西在動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,激光槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL裏有個機械木偶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這是機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,機動戰士為什麼會變的像遺跡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞！蹲下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,機動戰士的反應！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球應該沒有機動戰士的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,開槍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市內被擊中！為什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它自己在動 停不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停下來！\N怎樣停下來?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,中槍了！?  損毀情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,下次將直接命中我嗎！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我們迪安娜回歸軍的情報\N怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:09.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是\N駕駛艙的光並沒有完全消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.01,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼會動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我看能夠開動它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,起火啊！到處火光熊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:15.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哪裏起火！?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:33.60,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁微热还未减退\N微熱がさめないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:40.91,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低头少年的瞳孔\Nうつむく少年の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.38,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝望心海\N心の海みつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:50.44,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静地在微笑\静かにほほえんてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生 消逝\N生まれくるもの　消えてゆくもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:03.33,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宿命钟摆的两端\Nすべては宿命の振子の幅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:09.07,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过挫折的黑暗射进来\N挫折の闇を突き拔けみえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:14.48,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的光明\Nそれが光の真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.10,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:25.21,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着黎明献给被遗忘的星球\N夜明けとともに忘れ去られる星に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:27.82,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:35.09,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高的爱在那双细小的手里\N至上の愛は小さなその手の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不想姬艾爾和蘇絲亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被捲入戰火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 諾克斯市好像損毀嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,身在大屋的老爺也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,雖然基斯想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:54.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我卻坐上WHITE DOLL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,雖然沒有精神準備
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,次回 TURN A高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,節日之後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:05.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,戰爭之風刮起了

